    "Html": "Hi,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nI would like to also set a mouse over style, that overrides the value &quot;AlternatingRowBackground&quot; color - Is the solution above the recommended approach?&nbsp; Here is some of my xaml....<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&lt;tk:DataGrid x:Name=&quot;Grid&quot; SelectionUnit=&quot;FullRow&quot;<br>\r\nAlternatingRowBackground=&quot;#f9f9f9&quot; <br>\r\n<br>\r\n.....<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Style x:Key=&quot;DataGridRowStyle&quot; TargetType=&quot;{x:Type tk:DataGridRow}&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Style.Triggers&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Trigger Property=&quot;IsMouseOver&quot; Value=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Background&quot; Value=&quot;#FFFFFFE0&quot; /&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/Trigger&gt;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks!<br>\r\nJon<br>\r\n",
